          }}></path></svg></a>{`Is there a limit to how many alerts can group into a single incident?`}</h3>
    <p>{`Yes - incidents are limited to 1000 alerts each. After this limit is reached, a new incident will be created and subsequent alerts will continue grouping under the new incident.`}</p>

